replies.body:
I understand that whole concept of having 20 Champions in ranked but for this draft, can you pick free rotation champs?
If so, then the Number of Champions required should be lowered, or not? {{champion:32}}

Also, I'm not quite sure why you have to be level 10, but if thats the requirement, I guess it is.
Personally I think that will cause queue issues with everyone wanting to play draft.{{sticker:zombie-brand-facepalm}}

You.... you... mean I can ban champs in normal games now?

{{sticker:sg-syndra}} 
Stand before me monk, and **BURN!** {{champion:64}}

Ranked 3v3 player here, are you guys concerned at all about the fact that you will be testing normal draft on the same day / times as ranked 3v3? (Thursday and Friday nights)

The queue times are already pretty long and I'm a bit worried that testing another queue may make it worse. 
{{champion:78}}
